{
  "number": 83,
  "name": "سُورَةُ المُطَفِّفِينَ",
  "englishName": "Al-Mutaffifin",
  "ayahs": [
    {
      "number": 1,
      "text": "Woe to those who give less [than due],",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 587,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 2,
      "text": "Who, when they take a measure from people, take in full.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 587,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 3,
      "text": "But if they give by measure or by weight to them, they cause loss.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 587,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4,
      "text": "Do they not think that they will be resurrected",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 587,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5,
      "text": "For a tremendous Day -",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 587,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6,
      "text": "The Day when mankind will stand before the Lord of the worlds?",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 587,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 7,
      "text": "No! Indeed, the record of the wicked is in sijjeen.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 8,
      "text": "And what can make you know what is sijjeen?",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 9,
      "text": "It is [their destination recorded in] a register inscribed.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 10,
      "text": "Woe, that Day, to the deniers,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 11,
      "text": "Who deny the Day of Recompense.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 12,
      "text": "And none deny it except every sinful transgressor.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 13,
      "text": "When Our verses are recited to him, he says, \"Legends of the former peoples.\"",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 14,
      "text": "No! Rather, the stain has covered their hearts of that which they were earning.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 15,
      "text": "No! Indeed, from their Lord, that Day, they will be partitioned.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 16,
      "text": "Then indeed, they will [enter and] burn in Hellfire.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 17,
      "text": "Then it will be said [to them], \"This is what you used to deny.\"",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 18,
      "text": "No! Indeed, the record of the righteous is in 'illiyyun.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 19,
      "text": "And what can make you know what is 'illiyyun?",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 20,
      "text": "It is [their destination recorded in] a register inscribed",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 21,
      "text": "Which is witnessed by those brought near [to Allah].",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 22,
      "text": "Indeed, the righteous will be in pleasure",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 23,
      "text": "On adorned couches, observing.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 24,
      "text": "You will recognize in their faces the radiance of pleasure.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 25,
      "text": "They will be given to drink [pure] wine [which was] sealed.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 26,
      "text": "The last of it is musk. So for this let the competitors compete.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 27,
      "text": "And its mixture is of Tasneem,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 28,
      "text": "A spring from which those near [to Allah] drink.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 29,
      "text": "Indeed, those who committed crimes used to laugh at those who believed.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 30,
      "text": "And when they passed by them, they would exchange derisive glances.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 31,
      "text": "And when they returned to their people, they would return jesting.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 32,
      "text": "And when they saw them, they would say, \"Indeed, those are truly lost.\"",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 33,
      "text": "But they had not been sent as guardians over them.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 34,
      "text": "So Today those who believed are laughing at the disbelievers,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 35,
      "text": "On adorned couches, observing.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 589,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 36,
      "text": "Have the disbelievers [not] been rewarded [this Day] for what they used to do?",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 589,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    }
  ]
}